:0,"quote":{"pid":"21b4d0ae50c2592fe0ac1b3e4f024fc63bbf7676","tid":544030,"uid":78774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T06:54:49.000Z","msg":"Off Topic一問<br />\n係香港想打冰球有咩門路 睇過總會D course 都係俾小朋友學<br />\n<br />\n利申：廿幾歲 新手 只識向前溜冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:13:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.megaice.com.hk/tc/skating-school/lesson-information/ice-hockey.php#introduction\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.megaice.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fskating-school%2Flesson-information%2Fice-hockey.php%23introduction&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ed863d65\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.megaice.com.hk/tc/skating-school/lesson-information/ice-hockey.php#introduction</a><br />\n<br />\n可能有"},{"pid":"f3181c7a262da0390b8df1e0a6c3b7d7edbf4da9","tid":544030,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T15:00:26.000Z","msg":"A member of Russian FIB Executive committee Nikolai Valuev visited matches of the World championship. <br />\n<br />\n&quot;Loads of work to lay ahead in the Moscow region. My dream is, in particular, concerns the restoration of bandy in Saint-Petersburg &quot;, - told Nikolai Valuev.<br />\n<br />\nTo his mind, the inclusion of bandy in Olympic Games program will attract more people to go in for the sport.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Potentially bandy has been long ago capable to claim for and claims for the capacity of Olympic sport fulfilling all requirements and being, to put it that way, rather attractive from the view point of organization. Don't forget that arenas for speed skating which is presented at Winter Olympic Games may be platforms for bandy&quot;, - noted Nikolay Valuev."},{"pid":"f1354f89dbb3b4d6bf55aa03626b55bcc62e8756","tid":544030,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d5b30528023cc55cb8a214b9528889054a0f15","tid":544030,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T18:53:43.000Z","msg":"<strong>南北韓女子冰球聯隊首次訓練</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/c9414fa02d8a5b3e8b092cac10d3706a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fc9414fa02d8a5b3e8b092cac10d3706a.jpg&h=e8569153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n參加平昌冬奧的南北韓女子冰球聯隊首次一起訓練。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社報道，首場訓練在南韓鎮川國家代表選手村舉行，由聯隊主教練薩拉穆雷主持，35名兩韓冰球選手分為A、B兩組，上午分別訓練30分鐘，下午再進行對抗訓練。<br />\n<br />\n12名北韓運動員和助手等人是在上星期四抵達南韓，與南韓隊員一起練習。<br />\n<br />\n根據兩韓協議，冬奧每場比賽必須有3名北韓選手上場，兩韓運動員盡快磨合非常重要。<br />\n<br />\n聯隊將於2月4日與瑞典打熱身賽。冬奧首場賽事是2月10日將迎戰瑞士。"},{"pid":"8a5770f7fab605f408a7e7401bd6363f3a6f0d69","tid":544030,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T19:32:55.000Z","msg":"幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddee1439e1a07d5e505c3f6bfdff09a8f48a4ceb","tid":544030,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T19:57:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">乙組8強賽程<br />\n<br />\n蒙古 vs 中國<br />\n日本 vs 斯洛伐克<br />\n荷蘭 vs 烏克蘭<br />\n愛沙尼亞 vs 索馬利亞<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"e864ddffe49e7ad729d36e2f5a1e4f4d94d83077","tid":544030,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T20:04:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4MSaoSxt8c4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4MSaoSxt8c4&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=8dc99840\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4MSaoSxt8c4</a><br />\n美國對匈牙利<br />\n11點直播"},{"pid":"b165bb7e4b96d7b499d83364fb9cd9cae3d61c9e","tid":544030,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:29:11.000Z","msg":"打緊<br />\n美國 6-0 匈牙利"},{"pid":"962235b332332b121eb2a4d47b6bb0862ceb8ebc","tid":544030,"